com.cs309.loginscreen.Model

Interface IServerListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddTaskPresenter, AddUserPresenter, AllTaskPresenter, ChatPresenter, MyFriendsPresenter, VerificationPresenter

    public interface IServerListener
    Listener interface for Presenter classes. Implement this if you want to use the API to talk to the server. It handles all the success, error messages, and it works with our debug system.
